<subSubSection id="C331F4EFFFCF1D555053F851F985FECC" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B94A764FFCF1D555053F851F985FECC" blockId="17.[94,719,1978,2131]" lastBlockId="17.[794,1418,218,339]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<emphasis id="B95F7B76FFCF1D555053F851FDB0F84C" bold="true" box="[94,205,1978,2003]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Remarks:</emphasis>
Species described on a single male labelled ‘ 
<collectingCountry id="F33CE7F4FFCF1D55506CF831FDDFF86C" box="[97,162,2010,2035]" name="Brazil" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Brésil</collectingCountry>
, Santarem’, preserved in NHMB. No other specimens are known so far. The 
<typeStatus id="549019C6FFCF1D5551BCF811FF6BF78C" box="[433,534,2042,2067]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">holotype</typeStatus>
lacks some tarsi and last antennomeres. The specimens collected in 
<collectingCountry id="F33CE7F4FFCF1D555053F7D1FC7BF7CC" box="[94,262,2106,2131]" name="French Guiana" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
, initially named as 
<taxonomicName id="4C2BDCE7FFCF1D5551E7F7D1FFD5F7CC" authorityName="Brancucci" authorityYear="1981" box="[490,680,2106,2131]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="santaremensis">
<emphasis id="B95F7B76FFCF1D5551E7F7D1FFD5F7CC" box="[490,680,2106,2131]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">M. santaremensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by Constantin (2016), are similar to the male 
<typeStatus id="549019C6FFCF1D555508FF31F817FF6C" box="[1285,1386,218,243]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">holotype</typeStatus>
in the body shape and genitalia, but additional material reveals new elusive characters leading to the description of 
<taxonomicName id="4C2BDCE7FFCF1D555317FED1FECCFECC" authority="Biffi &amp; Constantin, 2018" authorityName="Biffi &amp; Constantin" authorityYear="2018" box="[794,945,314,339]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guyanensis" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis id="B95F7B76FFCF1D555317FED1FECCFECC" box="[794,945,314,339]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">M. guyanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A26CC60DFFCF1D5553BBFED1FE8DFECC" box="[950,1008,314,339]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C2BDCE7FFCF1D555428FED1F9C5FECC" authority="Biffi &amp; Constantin, 2018" authorityName="Biffi &amp; Constantin" authorityYear="2018" box="[1061,1208,314,339]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="orapuensis" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis id="B95F7B76FFCF1D555428FED1F9C5FECC" box="[1061,1208,314,339]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">M. orapuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A26CC60DFFCF1D5554B3FED1F985FECC" box="[1214,1272,314,339]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
